text: "Rush You" is a song by Australian rock band Baby Animals. It was released in August 1991 as their second single from their debut studio album Baby Animals (1991). The song peaked at number 30 on the ARIA Singles Chart. ==Track listings== Vinyl/CD single (25003) # "Rush You" – 4:10 # "Big Time Friends" – 4:54 ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" |- !
